description: The prisoner still refuses to confess. There’s nothing for it but more severe treatment from Mistress Vixen. She kicks him into submission, tramples him in her sharp stiletto thigh boots, making sure to dig and grind her heels into his flesh and then pisses over him and in his mouth. Degradation and brutality is the name of Mistress Vixen’s game and there’s no one better at it!
title: The Confession - Part 2
